</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation id="1342BBC7FF89FF92F3C3FE8EED15FEC4" box="[725,805,292,319]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="10.[172,205,1714,1736]" captionTargetBox="[256,1150,742,1692]" captionTargetId="figure-11@10.[253,1162,742,1695]" captionText="Fig. 10. Trioxys curvicaudus, ♀ (1–5) and Trioxys pallidus, ♀ (6–10): 1, 6 — antenna; 2, 7 — forewing; 3, 8 — propodeum; 4, 9 — petiole; 5 a, 5 b, 10 — ovipositor sheath and prongs. Рис. 10. Trioxys curvicaudus, ♀ (1–5) и Trioxys pallidus, ♀ (6–10): 1, 6 — усик; 2, 7 — переднее крыло; 3, 8 — проподеум; 4, 9 — стебелёк; 5 a, 5 b, 10 — створки яйцеклада и пронги." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6467470" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6467470/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="399">fig. 10</figureCitation>
